<p2> NBA games house four quarters lasting twelve minutes for a total run-time of 48 minute games. Although the average game length goes around half-an-hour due to a fifteen minute half time break and fouling. A foul in the NBA occurs when a player does something that breaks the rules like unncessary roughness. In recent years NBA basketball players have been shooting more three point shots than ever before. </p2>
