<h3> What makes the NBA standout from the rest? </h3>
<p4> The NBA is widely known around the world as the best and most profittable basketball league to play in. There have been debates suggesting that the NBA isn't "international" because of it's North American playing locations. To rebutal that argument; It's nearly impossible to find any basketball team outside of the NBA that can take on NBA championship teams.   </p4>
